Introduction/Business Problem section 

Problem: 
    In a large city like San Jose, a restaurateur is looking to open a restaurant in a neighborhood. Where will it be a success? 
Solution: 
    We will use the Foursquare API to explore neighborhoods in San Jose to find a place where a new restaurant can be a success.


More Information:
Many people who looking to open a restaurant can use this solution.
Here the target is restaurateur. 
A restaurateur would care about this solution because it will help them to uniquely find a location based on their interest to open a restaurant.
In such a big city and with so many competitors it is difficult to find a unique place to thrive. This solution will them with their needs and give them preferences to get a neighborhood where they can open their restaurant and get a good income flow since there will be a huge sale.
